.SH "NAME"
ata_port_detach \- Detach ATA port in preparation of device removal
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'void\ ata_port_detach('u
.BI "void ata_port_detach(struct\ ata_port\ *\ " "ap" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIap\fR
.RS 4
ATA port to be detached
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Detach all ATA devices and the associated SCSI devices of
\fIap\fR; then, remove the associated SCSI host\&.
\fIap\fR
is guaranteed to be quiescent on return from this function\&.
.PP
LOCKING: Kernel thread context (may sleep)\&.
